\"}]\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"GitHub Copilot：智能体觉醒——使用 GitHub Copilot Agent Mode 构建应用程序\",\"url\":\"https://reactor.microsoft.com/zh-cn/reactor/events/25296/\"},{\"title\":\"Microsoft AI Genius 第三季 | 从 Ignite 到生产：快速构建完整 AI 技术方案\",\"url\":\"https://reactor.microsoft.com/zh-cn/reactor/series/s-1577/\"},{\"title\":\"高效开发，快人一步——智能 GitHub Copilot 副驾驶® Agent Mode伴你左右\",\"url\":\"https://developer.microsoft.com/pt-br/reactor/events/26252/\"},{\"title\":\"高效开发，快人一步——智能 GitHub Copilot 副驾驶® Agent Mode伴你左右\",\"url\":\"https://developer.microsoft.com/it-it/reactor/events/26252/\"},{\"title\":\"Agentic AI, MCP, and spec-driven development\",\"url\":\"https://github.blog/developer-skills/agentic-ai-mcp-and-spec-driven-development-top-blog-posts-of-2025/\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub Copilot Agent Mode：提升开发效率的AI助手\",\"url\":\"https://m.php.cn/faq/1859293.html\"},{\"title\":\"AI Skills Fest Global Reactor Sessions\",\"url\":\"https://developer.microsoft.com/zh-cn/reactor/series/s-1499/\"},{\"title\":\"Visual Studio release notes\",\"url\":\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/visualstudio/releases/2022/release-notes\"},{\"title\":\"Visual Studio のリリース ノート\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/ja-jp/visualstudio/releases/2022/release-notes\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub Copilot 2025年8月最新更新！\",\"url\":\"https://cloud.tencent.com.cn/developer/article/2567708?policyId=1003\"}]\n\nBased on my web search, I found information about AI coding tools that were launched or announced in **February 2025**. Here are the key findings:\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 AI Coding Tools Launched in February 2025\n\n### 1. **Claude Code (by Anthropic)**\n- **Launch Date:** February 24, 2025\n- **What it is:** An \"agentic\" AI coding tool that runs directly in the developer's command-line terminal\n- **Key Features:**\n  - Built into the terminal and IDE (VS Code, JetBrains)\n  - Can analyze entire codebases across multiple files\n  - Can execute shell commands, run tests, and handle git workflows\n  - Iterates on its own output and can correct errors automatically\n  - Deep code awareness with agentic search capabilities\n  - Safe and controllable with confirmation prompts\n\n**Source:** Dev.to article mentions: *\"In late February 2025, Anthropic introduced Claude Code, an 'agentic' AI coding tool built into the developer's command-line terminal.\"*\n\n---\n\n### 2. **GitHub Copilot Agent Mode**\n- **Announcement:** Early February 2025\n- **What it is:** A new \"agent mode\" for GitHub Copilot\n- **Key Features:**\n  - Can iterate on its own output\n  - Automatically recognizes and corrects errors\n  - Handles multi-step coding tasks from start to finish\n  - Analyzes codebases and reads relevant files\n  - Runs terminal commands and tests\n  - Responds to compilation and lint errors\n  - Monitors terminal and test output in a loop until task completion\n\n**Source:** Dev.to article mentions: *\"In early February 2025, GitHub announced a new 'agent mode' for Copilot that allows it to iterate on its own output and correct errors automatically.\"*\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Note About Product Hunt\n\nI was unable to find direct results from `producthunt.com` specifically about these launches in my search. The search results primarily referenced:\n\n- Blog articles and news sites (CSDN, Dev.to, etc.)\n- GitHub's official blog\n- Anthropic documentation\n\nTo find the actual Product Hunt pages for these tools, you may need to:\n1. Visit producthunt.com directly\n2. Search for \"Claude Code\" or \"GitHub Copilot Agent Mode\"\n3. Filter by February 2025 launch dates\n\n---\n\nWould you like me to perform a more targeted search or provide additional details about either of these tools?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
