ion and modification\n- Can run Shell/Git/test commands with user authorization\n- Provides deep code awareness through \"agentic search\"\n- Enables multi-file consistency editing for refactoring and feature development\n\n### 3. **Related Context**\nThe same period (early 2025) saw similar AI coding tool announcements:\n- GitHub announced a new \"agent mode\" for Copilot in early February 2025\n- Replit's Ghostwriter Chat launched in January 2025 as one of the first conversational AI programmers integrated into an online IDE\n\nThe search results indicate that **Claude Code was officially introduced by Anthropic in late February 2025**, positioning it as part of the wave of agentic AI coding tools that emerged in early 2025.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
