ent\n3. **Inspector automatically writes these changes to your codebase**\n4. **Push directly to your code repository**\n\n### Value Proposition:\n- Eliminate design handoffs\n- No need for traditional design-to-development handover processes\n- Direct integration with code repositories\n- Works seamlessly with popular AI coding assistants\n\n### Keywords Associated:\n- Visual editor (视觉编辑器)\n- AI assistant (AI助手)\n- Claude Code, Codex, Cursor\n- UI element editing (UI元素)\n- Code changes (代码变更)\n- Design delivery (设计交付)\n- Code repository (代码仓库)\n\nInspector appears to be a bridge tool that allows designers and developers to make visual changes that are automatically translated into code changes through AI assistants, particularly Claude Code. It was featured prominently on Product Hunt in early February 2026 as a top product.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
